Class MemoryJavaFileObject

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class MemoryJavaFileObject
extends Object
implements JavaFileObject
    A JavaFileObject held in memory. This is almost exactly the same as the JavaSourceFromString class in the JavaCompiler documentation.
